        <title><![CDATA[The Aggregation framework]]></title>
        <link>http://xameeramir.github.io/mongodb-aggregation-framework/</link>
        <pubDate>2016-09-24T00:00:00+00:00</pubDate>
        <dc:creator></dc:creator>
